objects.name: ChromeLoader
objects.description: In January 2022, a new browser hijacker / adware campaign named ChromeLoader bursted. Despite using a simple phishing mechanism, the malware was widely spread, potentially leaking data of thousands of users and organizations. The authors of this malware decided to use a browser extension as their final payload- not a common decision between malware authors. This extension serves as an adware and as an infostealer, leaking all of the user’s queries to search engines in addition to his chrome account credentials.
